AGRICULTURE CODE

previously been convicted of an offense under that subsection, in
which event the offense is a Class B misdemeanor.
Added by Acts 2009, 81st Leg., R.S., Ch. 948 (H.B. 3330), Sec. 1, eff.
September 1, 2009.

